Viruses. In this study, all viruses were derived from the virus repository of the EU/OIE/FAO international reference laboratory for AI at the Veterinary Laboratories Agency, New Haw, Addlestone, Weybridge, Woking, Surrey, UK (Table 1, Table 2, Table 3
). Representative strains were derived principally from avian hosts to include H subtypes 1–15 but also included some viruses from mammalian hosts. Several other clinically relevant viral pathogens were used for specificity testing (listed in Table 4, Table 5, Table 6
).
